<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>{include file ='library/admin_html_head.lbi'}</head>

<body class="iframe_body">
<div class="warpper">
    <div class="title">订单 - {$ur_here}</div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="explanation" id="explanation">
            <div class="ex_tit"><i class="sc_icon"></i><h4>操作提示</h4><span id="explanationZoom" title="收起提示"></span></div>
            <ul>
                <li>标识“<em>*</em>”的选项为必填项，其余为选填项。</li>
                <li>添加订单流程为：选择商城已有会员-选择商品加入订单-确认订单金额-填写收货信息-添加配送方式-选择支付方式-添加发票-查看费用信息-完成。</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="flexilist mt30">
            <div class="common-content">
                {if $step eq "user"}
                <form name="theForm" action="order.php?act=step_post&step={$step}&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}" method="post" onsubmit="return checkUser()">
                    <div class="common-content">
                        <div class="step">
                            <div class="step_title">
                                <i class="ui-step"></i><h3>填写用户</h3>
                                <div class="fr">
                                    <div class="fbutton mt5 mr0"><div class="piliang" title="批量添加订单"><span><i class="icon icon-copy"></i><a href="mc_order.php">批量添加订单</a></span></div></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step_info">
                                <div class="order_user_select">
                                    <div class="anonymous_user checkbox_user checked_user">
                                        <div class="checkbox_item">
                                            <input type="radio" name="anonymous" value="1" class="ui-radio" id="anonymous_user" checked />
                                            <label for="anonymous_user" class="ui-radio-label">{$lang.anonymous}</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="register_user checkbox_user">
                                        <div class="checkbox_item">
                                            <input type="radio" name="anonymous" value="0" class="ui-radio" id="register_user" />
                                            <label for="register_user" class="ui-radio-label">{$lang.by_useridname}</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="register_user_warp">
                                            <div class="search">
                                                <input type="text" name="keyword" class="text mr0" placeholder="会员名称/编号" autocomplete="off" readonly />
                                                <input type="button" class="select_btn" name="search" onclick="searchUser();" />
                                                <div id="user" class="imitate_select select_w260">
                                                    <div class="cite">会员名称</div>
                                                    <ul style="display: none;">
                                                        <li class="li_not">请先搜索会员名称</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                    <input name="user" type="hidden" value="" id="user_val">
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="div_readonly"></div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="notic">
                                                <strong>注意：</strong>搜索结果只显示前20条记录，如果没有找到相应会员，请更精确地查找。<br>
                                                另外，如果该会员是从论坛注册的且没有在商城登录过，也无法找到，需要先在商城登录。
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="goods_btn">
                            <input type="button" value="{$lang.button_cancel}" class="btn btn35 btn_blue" onclick="location.href='order.php?act=process&func=cancel_order&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}'" />
                            <input name="submit" type="submit" class="btn btn35 blue_btn" value="{$lang.button_next}" />
                        </div>   
                    </div>				
                </form>
                {elseif $step eq "goods"}
                <div class="step">
                    <form name="theForm" action="order.php?act=step_post&step=edit_goods&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}" method="post">
                        <div class="step_info">
                            <div class="add_goods_list">
                                <table class="table" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th width="30%" class="tc">{$lang.goods_name}</th>
                                        <th width="10%">{$lang.goods_sn}</th>
                                        <th width="12%">{$lang.goods_price}</th>
                                        <th width="10%">{$lang.goods_number}</th>
                                        <th width="13%">{$lang.goods_attr}</th>
                                        <th width="10%">{$lang.subtotal}</th>
                                        <th width="5%">{$lang.handler}</th>
                                        <th class="total tc" width="10%" rowspan="3"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="submit()"><i class="icon icon-refresh"></i></a><span>{$lang.label_total}&nbsp;&nbsp;{$goods_amount}</span><input name="goods_count" type="hidden" value="{$smarty.foreach.goods.total}" /></th>
                                    </tr>
                                    {foreach from=$goods_list item=goods name="goods"}
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info">
                                            {if $goods.goods_id gt 0 && $goods.extension_code neq 'package_buy'}
                                                <a href="javascript:;" onclick="getGoodsInfo({$goods.goods_id});">{$goods.goods_name}</a>
                                            {elseif $goods.goods_id gt 0 && $goods.extension_code eq 'package_buy'}
                                                {$goods.goods_name}
                                            {/if}   
                                        </td>
                                        <td>{$goods.goods_sn}<input name="rec_id[]" type="hidden" value="{$goods.rec_id}" /></td>
                                        <td>
                                            <input name="goods_price[]" type="text" class="text w50" autocomplete="off" value="{$goods.goods_price}" />
                                            <input name="goods_id[]" type="hidden" class="text w50" autocomplete="off" value="{$goods.goods_id}" />
                                            <input name="goods_attr[]" type="hidden" class="text w50" autocomplete="off" value="{$goods.goods_attr}" />
                                        </td>
                                        <td><input type="text" class="text w50" name="goods_number[]" autocomplete="off" value="{$goods.goods_number}"/></td>
                                        <td>{$goods.goods_attr}</td>
                                        <td>{$goods.subtotal}</td>
                                        <td><a href="javascript:confirm_redirect(confirm_drop, 'order.php?act=process&func=drop_order_goods&rec_id={$goods.rec_id}&step_act={$step_act}&order_id={$order_id}')">{$lang.drop}</a></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    {foreachelse}
                                    <tr><td class="no-records" colspan="7">{$lang.no_records}</td></tr>
                                    {/foreach}
                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <form name="goodsForm" action="order.php?act=step_post&step=add_goods&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}" method="post" onsubmit="return addToOrder()">
                        <div class="goods_search_filer">
                            <strong>{$lang.search_goods}</strong>
                            <input type="text" name="keyword" class="text w120" autocomplete="off" placeholder="编号/名称/货号" />
                            {if $warehouse_list}
                                <strong>{$lang.warehouse}</strong>
                                <div class="select">
                                    <div id="warehouse_id" class="imitate_select select_w170">
                                        <div class="cite">{$lang.please_select}</div>
                                        <ul style="display: none;">
                                            {foreach from=$warehouse_list item=list}
                                                <li><a href="javascript:;" data-value="{$list.region_id}" class="ftx-01">{$list.region_name}</a></li>
                                            {/foreach}
                                        </ul>
                                        <input name="warehouse_id" type="hidden" value="" id="warehouse_id_val">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <strong>{$lang.region}</strong>
                                <div class="select">
                                    <div id="area_id" class="imitate_select select_w170">
                                        <div class="cite">{$lang.please_select}</div>
                                        <ul style="display: none;" >
                                            <li class="li_not">请先选择仓库</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <input name="area_id" type="hidden" value="" id="area_id_val">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            {/if}
                            <a href="javascript:;" name="search" onclick="searchGoods();" class="btn btn30 blue_btn mr20"><i class="icon icon-search"></i>{$lang.button_search}</a>

                            <div class="select" id="search_result">
                                <div id="goodslist" class="imitate_select select_w500">
                                    <div class="cite">{$lang.please_select}</div>
                                    <ul style="display:none;">
                                        <li class="li_not">请先搜索商品</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <input name="goodslist" type="hidden" value="" id="goodslist_val">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="goods_info_add">
                            <div class="goods_info_desc">
                                <table class="table">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">{$lang.goods_name}</td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right first"><div id="goods_name"></div></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">{$lang.goods_sn}</td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right"><div id="goods_sn"></div></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">{$lang.category}</td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right"><div id="goods_cat"></div></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">{$lang.brand}</td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right"><div id="goods_brand"></div></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">{$lang.goods_price}</td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right"><div id="add_price" class="checkbox_items"></div></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">{$lang.goods_attr}<input type="hidden" name="spec_count" value="0" /></td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right"><div id="goods_attr"></div></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">{$lang.storage}</td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right"><div id="goods_storage"></div></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">{$lang.goods_number}</td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right"><input name="add_number" class="text w80" type="text" autocomplete="off" value="1"></td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="goods_info_left">加入订单</td>
                                        <td class="goods_info_right last">
                                            <input name="add_goods" type="submit" value="{$lang.add_to_order}" class="btn btn30 red_btn" />
                                            <input name="model_attr" value="0" type="hidden" />
                                            <input name="attr_price" value="0" type="hidden" />
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </div>                           
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <form action="order.php?act=step_post&step=goods&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}" method="post">
                        <div class="goods_btn" id="button-info">
                            <input type="button" value="{$lang.button_cancel}" class="btn btn35 btn_blue" onclick="location.href='order.php?act=process&func=cancel_order&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}'" />
                            <input type="button" class="btn btn35 btn_blue" onclick="history.back()" value="上一步">
                            <input name="{if $step_act eq 'add'}next{else}finish{/if}" type="submit" class="btn btn35 blue_btn" value="{if $step_act eq 'add'}{$lang.button_next}{else}{$lang.button_submit}{/if}" />
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                {elseif $step eq "consignee"}
                <form name="theForm" action="order.php?act=step_post&step={$step}&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}" method="post" onsubmit="return checkConsignee()">
                    <div class="step">
                    	<div class="step_title pb5">
                            <i class="ui-step"></i>
                            <h3 class="fl">请填写收货信息</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step_content step_content_items">
                            {if $address_list}
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.address_list}</div>
                                <div class="step_value">
                                    <div id="addresslist" class="imitate_select select_w320">
                                        <div class="cite">{$order.consignee}{$order.email}{$order.address}</div>
                                        <ul style="display: none;">
                                            {foreach from=$address_list item=address}
                                                <li><a href='javascript:;' data-value='{$address.address_id}' class='ftx-01'>{$address.consignee|escape}{$address.email}{$address.address|escape}{$address.tel|escape}</a></li>
                                            {/foreach}
                                        </ul>
                                        <input name="addresslist" type="hidden" value="" id="addresslist_val">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            {/if}
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.require_field}{$lang.label_consignee}</div>
                                <div class="step_value"><input type="text" name="consignee" value="{$order.consignee}" id="consignee" class="text" autocomplete="off" /></div>
                            </div>
                            {if $exist_real_goods}
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.require_field}{$lang.label_area}</div>
                                <div class="step_value">
                                    <div class="level_linkage">
                                        <div id="dlcountry" class="ui-dropdown smartdropdown alien">
                                            <input type="hidden" value="{$order.country}" name="country" id="selcountry">
                                            <div class="txt">国家</div>
                                            <i class="down u-dropdown-icon"></i>
                                            <div class="options clearfix" style="max-height:300px;">
                                                {foreach from=$country_list item=list}
                                                <span class="liv" data-text="{$list.region_name}" data-type="1"  data-value="{$list.region_id}">{$list.region_name}</span>
                                                {/foreach}
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div id="dlProvinces" class="ui-dropdown smartdropdown alien">
                                            <input type="hidden" value="{$order.province}" name="province" id="selProvinces">
                                            <div class="txt">省/直辖市</div>
                                            <i class="down u-dropdown-icon"></i>
                                            <div class="options clearfix" style="max-height:300px;">
                                                {foreach from=$province_list item=list}
                                                <span class="liv" data-text="{$list.region_name}" data-type="2"  data-value="{$list.region_id}">{$list.region_name}</span>
                                                {/foreach}
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div id="dlCity" class="ui-dropdown smartdropdown alien">
                                            <input type="hidden" value="{$order.city}" name="city" id="selCities">
                                            <div class="txt">市</div>
                                            <i class="down u-dropdown-icon"></i>
                                            <div class="options clearfix" style="max-height:300px;">
                                                {foreach from=$city_list item=list}
                                                <span class="liv" data-text="{$list.region_name}" data-value="{$list.region_id}">{$list.region_name}</span>
                                                {/foreach}
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div id="dlRegion" class="ui-dropdown smartdropdown alien">
                                            <input type="hidden" value="{$order.district}" name="district" id="selDistricts">
                                            <div class="txt">区/县</div>
                                            <i class="down u-dropdown-icon"></i>
                                            <div class="options clearfix" style="max-height:300px;">
                                                {foreach from=$district_list item=list}
                                                <span class="liv" data-text="{$list.region_name}" data-value="{$list.region_id}">{$list.region_name}</span>
                                                {/foreach}
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            {/if}
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.require_field}{$lang.label_email}</div>
                                <div class="step_value"><input type="text" name="email" id="email" value="{$order.email}" class="text" autocomplete="off" /></div>
                            </div>
                            {if $exist_real_goods}
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.require_field}{$lang.label_address}</div>
                                <div class="step_value"><input type="text" name="address" id="address"  value="{$order.address}" class="text" autocomplete="off" /></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.label_zipcode}</div>
                                <div class="step_value"><input type="text" name="zipcode" id="zipcode" value="{$order.zipcode}" class="text" autocomplete="off" /></div>
                            </div>
                            {/if}
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.label_tel}</div>
                                <div class="step_value"><input type="text" name="tel" id="tel" value="{$order.tel}" class="text" autocomplete="off" /></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.label_mobile}</div>
                                <div class="step_value"><input type="text" name="mobile" id="mobile" value="{$order.mobile}" class="text" autocomplete="off" /></div>
                            </div>
                            {if $exist_real_goods}
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.label_sign_building}</div>
                                <div class="step_value"><input type="text" name="sign_building" id="sign_building" value="{$order.sign_building}" class="text" autocomplete="off" /></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="step_label">{$lang.label_best_time}</div>
                                <div class="step_value"><input type="text" name="best_time" id="best_time" value="{$order.best_time}" class="text" autocomplete="off" /></div>
                            </div>
                            {/if}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="goods_btn">
                        <input type="button" value="{$lang.button_cancel}" class="btn btn35 btn_blue" onclick="location.href='order.php?act=process&func=cancel_order&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}'" />
                        {if $step_act eq "add"}{if $step_act eq "add"}<input type="button" value="{$lang.button_prev}" class="btn btn35 btn_blue" onclick="history.back()" />{/if}{/if}
                        <input name="{if $step_act eq 'add'}next{else}finish{/if}" type="submit" class="btn btn35 blue_btn" value="{if $step_act eq 'add'}{$lang.button_next}{else}{$lang.button_submit}{/if}" />
                    </div>
                </form>
                {elseif $step eq "shipping"}
                <form name="theForm" action="order.php?act=step_post&step={$step}&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}" method="post" onsubmit="return checkShipping()">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step_title pb5">
                            <i class="ui-step"></i>
                            <h3 class="fl">添加配送方式</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step_info">
                            <div class="list-div" id="list-div">
                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr>
                                            <th width="10%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.name}</div></th>
                                            <th width="45%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.desc}</div></th>
                                            <th width="10%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.region}</div></th>
                                            <th width="10%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.shipping_fee}</div></th>
                                            <th width="10%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.free_money}</div></th>
                                            <th width="10%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.insure}</div></th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                      {foreach from=$shipping_list item=shipping}
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><div class="tDiv"><div class="checkbox_item"><input name="shipping" type="radio" class="ui-radio" value="{$shipping.shipping_id}" id="shipping_{$shipping.shipping_id}" {if $order.shipping_id eq $shipping.shipping_id}checked{/if} onclick="" /><label for="shipping_{$shipping.shipping_id}" class="ui-radio-label">{$shipping.shipping_name}</label></div></td>
                                            <td><div class="tDiv">{$shipping.shipping_desc}</div></td>
                                            <td><div class="tDiv">{$shipping.parent_name}&nbsp;&nbsp;{$shipping.region_name}</div></td>
                                            <td>
                                                <div class="tDiv">
                                                    {$shipping.format_shipping_fee}
                                                    {if $shipping.freight_model}
                                                        {if $shipping.ru_count > 1}
                                                            <br/><em style="color:#CA0000">其中：
                                                            {foreach from=$shipping.ru_list item=list}
                                                            （{$list.warehouse_name}：{$list.shipping.configure_price}）<br/>
                                                            {/foreach}
                                                            </em>
                                                        {/if}
                                                    {/if}
                                                </div>
                                            </td>
                                            <td>
                                                <div class="tDiv">
                                                    {if $shipping.freight_model}
                                                        <em style="color:#CA0000">
                                                        {foreach from=$shipping.ru_list item=list}
                                                        （{$list.warehouse_name}：{$list.shipping.free_money}）<br/>
                                                        {/foreach}
                                                        </em>
                                                    {else}
                                                        {$shipping.free_money}
                                                    {/if}
                                                </div>
                                            </td>
                                            <td><div class="tDiv">{$shipping.insure}</div></td>
                                        </tr>
                                      {foreachelse}
                                        <tr>
                                            <td colspan="12" align="center"><div class="tDiv">请查看地区信息是否输入正确或改地区不支持配送</div></td>
                                        </tr>
                                      {/foreach}
                                    </tbody>
                                    <tfoot>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td colspan="12">
                                                <div class="tDiv">
                                                    <input type="checkbox" name="insure" class="ui-checkbox" id="baojia" value="1" {if $order.insure_fee > 0}checked{/if} />
                                                    <label for="baojia" class="ui-label">{$lang.want_insure}</label>
                                                </div>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tfoot>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="goods_btn">
                        {if $step_act eq "add"}<input type="button" value="{$lang.button_prev}" class="btn btn35 btn_blue" onclick="history.back()" />{/if}
                        <input name="{if $step_act eq 'add'}next{else}finish{/if}" type="submit" class="btn btn35 blue_btn" value="{if $step_act eq 'add'}{$lang.button_next}{else}{$lang.button_submit}{/if}" />
                        <input type="button" value="{$lang.button_cancel}" class="btn btn35 btn_blue" onclick="location.href='order.php?act=process&func=cancel_order&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}'" />
                    </div>
                </form>	
                {elseif $step eq "payment"}					
                <form name="theForm" action="order.php?act=step_post&step={$step}&order_id={$order_id}&step_act={$step_act}" method="post">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step_title pb5">
                            <i class="ui-step"></i>
                            <h3 class="fl">选择支付方式</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="step_info">
                            <div class="list-div" id="list-div">
                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr>
                                            <th width="10%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.name}</div></th>
                                            <th width="80%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.desc}</div></th>
                                            <th width="10%"><div class="tDiv">{$lang.pay_fee}</div></th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        {foreach from=$payment_list item=payment}
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><div class="tDiv"><div class="checkbox_item"><input type="radio" class="ui-radio" name="payment" value="{$payment.pay_id}" id="payment_{$payment.pay_id}" {if $order.pay_id eq $payment.pay_id}checked{/if} /><label class="ui-radio-label" for="payment_{$payment.pay_id}">{$payment.pay_name}</label></div></td>
                                            <td><div class="tDiv">{$payment.pay_desc}</div></td>
                                            <td><div class="tDiv">{$payment.pay_fee}</div></td>
